Package com.irurueta.navigation.inertial.calibration.noise

package com.irurueta.navigation.inertial.calibration.noise
Contains classes related to noise level estimation. Noise level estimation can be used by a static interval detector to determine periods of time when body where IMU is attached is static and when it is moving.
  • Related Packages
